1. "Molim vas da mi *poklonite* malo vremena." (Please give me some of your time.)
2. "Oni su *poklonili* veliku količinu novca za dobrotvorne svrhe." (They donated a large amount of money to charity.)
3. "Danas sam dobila mnogo *poklona* za rođendan." (Today I received many gifts for my birthday.)
4. "Nismo sigurni šta da *poklonimo* našem učitelju za Dan učitelja." (We're not sure what to give our teacher for Teacher's Day.)
5. "Ove godine ćemo *pokloniti* naš dom nekome ko ga više treba." (This year we will give our home to someone who needs it more.)
6. "Mama mi je *poklonila* novi džemper za Božić." (My mom gave me a new sweater for Christmas.)
7. "Svake godine *poklanjam* novac u humanitarne svrhe." (Every year I donate money to charity.)
8. "Oni *poklanjaju* svoje vrijeme i trud za dobrobit zajednice." (They volunteer their time and effort for the benefit of the community.)
9. "Nadam se da ćeš mi *pokloniti* svoje povjerenje." (I hope you will give me your trust.)
10. "Moja baka mi je *poklonila* zbirku bajki za rođendan." (My grandmother gave me a collection of fairy tales for my birthday.)